# AI/ML Internship – Day 5: Natural Language Processing & Chatbot

## Overview

Day 5 introduced the fundamentals of Natural Language Processing (NLP) through practical Python implementations. The session focused on text preprocessing techniques and building a simple rule-based chatbot.

### Topics Covered

* Text tokenization
* Stopword removal
* Stemming
* Lemmatization
* Introduction to NLP using NLTK
* Rule-based chatbot development

### Practical Work

* Processed text using NLTK libraries
* Implemented tokenization, stemming, and lemmatization
* Built a chatbot capable of responding to predefined user queries using conditional logic

